mage/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/umuntho.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Muntho</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/27/02 9:37:29 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=23058.topic>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> PoG </span><hr size=1> Pretty much and empty zone on my server and probably a whole lot more.<br><br>You have been selected by VI to be part of a group, your mission is to provide VI with some ideas (more content?) to get people to "want" to come to this underutilized zone.   <p>---------------<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=78166">Muntho</a><br>Sorceror of  <a href="http://pub4.ezboard.com/bthehaven">The Haven</a><br>Karana Server</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/urunetheborrower.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rune the Borrower</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/27/02 10:45:18 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=23058.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PoG </span><hr size=1> LOL<br><br>My guild went up there last night with a few friends. With chain drops as slow as they are in ToV we felt that perhaps we could get some armor for the Rogues and Shamen.<br><br>In 6 hours of cleraring we got 5 drops. Two were Beast Master drops (none on raid), 1 'chanter bracer that the 46 chanter didn't even want, 1 Monk hat that was left to rot (we had 4 monks 53-60) and a Cleric crown that a high 40s guest (not even in full EM yet) looted.<br><br>We did get a fair number of gems, each cleric went home laden with trinkets and about a dozen spells (half of which may be useful).<br><br>There is risk in this zone but I fail to see the reward.<br><br>Yes PoG is cleared regularly by the &quot;Ubers&quot; but that is ONLY to get to Tunare. IF they get any drops they most probably let it rot or give it to their #5 twinks.<br><br>If VI/Sony wants this zone used for anything other than a stageing ground to get to Tunare they need to up the drop rate just a little bit. <p>Runehammer Trollsbane<BR>Assassin of Cazik-Thule<BR><BR>Runesword<BR>Shadowblade of Gawain<BR>"I yam what I yam."<BR>Popeye</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usaevanjnoir.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Saevan JNoir</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Safehouse Supporter</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/27/02 10:46:21 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=23058.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PoG </span><hr size=1> I like it the way it is, a place for evils (and wannabe evils) to squash Tunare's minions. Our small band of 12 to 18 mid-50's does well up there, without getting pushed out by uber guilds.<br><br>There are lots of other underutilized zones to harrass ... er, improve. <br><br> <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=10371>Saevan J’Noir - Teir'Dal Blackguard</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=nenjindarkeyes>Nenjin Darkeyes</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/27/02 10:54:38 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=23058.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PoG </span><hr size=1> The loot is good loot........the drops rates are just crap. <br>And a wipe is a total pain in the ass because of the PoGs.<br>Not that I dislike PoG, but for the amount of effort it can require, the drops should be better IMO. <p>Nenjin Darkeyes<BR>55th lvl Blackguard of One Hundred Swords<BR>Xegony<BR>"Dont open your eyes, you wont like what you see. The devil's of Truth steal the souls of the free."--Trent Reznor</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/umuntho.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Muntho</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/27/02 12:43:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=23058.topic&index=4>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PoG </span><hr size=1> Was thinking they should add like 5 or 6 cave areas like they have in Umbral.  Areas with no faction hits. <p>---------------<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=78166">Muntho</a><br>Sorceror of  <a href="http://pub4.ezboard.com/bthehaven">The Haven</a><br>Karana Server</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ukizdean.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kizdean</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/globalBlack.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><b