font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=23058.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.shaw.ca/sjgardner/Images/celeris2.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Protectors of the Glade</span><hr size=1> Overall random drops in PoG are pretty bad indeed.  Still, the nameds are guaranteed BPs or leggings and are quite possible with a small raid force.  Some of the peices up there are pretty darn good but if you are ToV capable then your time would indeed be better served hunting in the wing of your choice. <p><center><b><font color=RED><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=78504>Celeris Tujimson</a><br>Blackguard of The Nameless<br></font></b><font color=CYAN size=2><i>"The church is near but the road is icy; the bar is far away but I'll walk carefully." ~Russian Proverb</i> </font></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ucartmean.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Cartmean</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_ball.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/27/02 5:26:39 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=23058.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PoG </span><hr size=1> other then tunare PoG is a joke <p><a href= http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=28164> Cartmean</a> <BR>59 Rez Whore <BR>*da pope*<BR><BR><a href= http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=5182> Alldar</a> <BR>35 Rogue <BR><BR><a href= http://www.finchmusic.com/finch_pc/finchpostcard.html>FINCH - Falling in to Place</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3